<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>8 SPEED, 9 SPEED, AND 13 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON SERIES - INSTALL - SLAVE VALVE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="4">
        <title>SLAVE VALVE</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If previously removed, install the air line fittings on the slave valve (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018cs">Figure 430</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018cs" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018cs" filename="../figg13/G13018cs.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 429. Install Air Line Fittings on Slave Valve</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the spring on the shank of the actuating pin and insert in the bore of the
                transmission case (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018ct">Figure 431</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018ct" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018ct" filename="../figg13/G13018ct.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 430. Install Spring on Shank of Actuating Pin</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the hat-type alignment sleeve in the bore of the slave valve (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018cu">Figure 432</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018cu" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018cu" filename="../figg13/G13018cu.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 431. Install Hat-Type Alignment Sleeve</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Position gasket on the valve mounting surface and install the slave valve on the case,
                inserting the end of the actuating pin into the alignment sleeve (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018cv">Figure 433</hotlnk>). Secure the valve to case with the four bolts. Apply
                Loctite 242 to the bolt threads and tighten evenly to 8 to 12 ft-lbs. (11 to 16 Nm).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018cv" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018cv" filename="../figg13/G13018cv.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 432. Secure Valve to Case With Bolts</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
